_sText:
To change the amount of kills gained, go to the game_score (called end_score) and edit the amount of points to give. 

To enable the trigger_multiple from start, set it to start enabled, delete the button, and delete the output that disables end_score_giver 
You can delete the point_servercommand if you want, make sure you delete it's input too.

No need to credit, highly appreciated if you do though!

*NOTE*
the screenshot shows me saying that I've gotten those kills, on a real server with admin isntalled Console will say it.
